# AGENTS.md

> Agent entry point. Read `.agents/` guides before making changes.

**Dev command:** `{{devCommand}}`

## Core Rules

- Follow existing project structure and patterns — infer from codebase, do not invent new ones.
- Prefer minimal, focused diffs. Do not refactor unrelated code.
- Never commit secrets, API keys, or credentials.
- Verify changes before claiming work is complete.

## Project Guides

For a project-tailored map of layers and conventions, run:

```
bunx github:fajaralhakim/agent-kit analyze . --write
```

That generates `.agents/architecture.md`, `.agents/code-conventions.md`, and per-layer guides based on your codebase.

Generic references:

| Guide | When to read |
|-------|--------------|
| `.agents/mcp-guide.md` | Setting up MCP servers (Atlassian, Figma, Context7) |
| `.agents/mcp-registry.md` | Available MCP integrations |

